cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.CY 

This paper focuses on cybersecurity and data sharing, which falls under the category of "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security). The use of cryptographic tools and privacy-preserving techniques suggests a focus on "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms). The use of a real-world dataset and experimentation suggests a focus on "cs.DB" (Databases) and the study of collaborative initiatives suggests a focus on "cs.CY" (Computers and Society).
